About this item

  • Menopause Relief: All-in-one acupressure wrist band provides natural relief for hot flashes, night sweats, stress, mood swings, sleep disturbances, irritability, headaches, fatigue, brain fog, joint pain and more. The perfect gift for women going through perimenopause and menopause
  • Natural Ingredients: 100% natural and non-toxic. Our herbal blend contains clary sage essential oil designed to provide a soothing and calming effect on the body and mind. Breathe in the scent!
  • Find Your Perfect Size: Our stretch acupressure bracelet is soft and comfortable, allowing for all-day wear. Slip it on and forget about it! See product pictures for sizing info.
  • Easy to Use: Simply slip on the bracelet and adjust to your preferred acupoints on your wrist. The acupressure points work to stimulate energy meridians and improve blood circulation. Use it at home, work or on the go.
  • Premium Quality: Handcrafted with love in the USA. Our bracelets are made from the highest quality materials and are designed to provide long-lasting relief. Backed by a 100% satisfaction guarantee.

5 Stars

It works for me.

I was skeptical at first. But within about 24 hours I noticed a difference. Now , I no longer get hot flashes.

Clary Sage & Stress Relief

A 2014 study published in Phytotherapy Research found that inhaling clary sage oil reduced cortisol levels by 36% and supported thyroid balance. The study, conducted on postmenopausal women, also noted a statistically significant calming effect, suggesting potential benefits for stress and mood support.

Acupressure & Aromatherapy – Targeted Wellness Support

Use our color-coded hand guide to find key acupressure points for hot flashes, mood balance, stress, nausea, and night sweats. Pairing acupressure with aromatherapy enhances relaxation and wellness. Designed for easy wear, allowing you to customize relief based on your needs.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
